data.description: Welcome home to this single-family house on Liem Circle in Springdale Arkansas! This home is located in a quiet, reserved neighborhood with kind neighbors. This is a high-value listing due to its location with businesses, restaurant options, and schools all within a 2–3-mile radius. This home has a beautiful large backyard, perfect for pets and kids. Its internal dark wood floorings are perfect for the traditional style look with the painted white walls of the living room to complement them. Home is less than 5 minutes away from your favorite coffee shop and just 2 minutes away from your kid's school (Central Jr. High & Springdale High School). Make this your home now!
